==English==

===Adjective===
'''sour'''
# having an [[acid]], [[sharp]] or [[tangy]] [[taste]]
# made [[rancid]] by [[fermentation]] etc
# [[tasting]] or [[smelling]] rancid
# [[peevish]] or [[bad-tempered]]
#(''of soil'') excessively acid and thus [[infertile]]
#(''of petroleum'') containing excess [[sulphur]]
